Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:08.32,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You know about neurosis? Wow, Lain. You’re going to have to start counseling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:12.26,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I know the word, not its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.30,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What kind of image?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.12,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,The mind changes and becomes distorted?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:20.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yes. You’ve got the general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.42,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,That’s awful. You won’t teach me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.04,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:28.02,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I’m really telling you that you got the general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:36.42,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Neurosis is a state in which there is nothing wrong with a person physically, yet the person has irrational fears and perceives threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:39.70,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This places a lot of stress on the person and makes her feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.48,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It’s only inside of their heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:45.52,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We used to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:50.90,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But after a lot of research, we think that an imbalance of the autonomic nerves in the brain is related to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:56.06,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What I mean is, something is wrong in the body, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:01.90,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We used to categorize physical symptoms as psychosomatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:08.36,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But we’ve been finding more and more that conditions we thought were only of the mind involve the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.60,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Psychosomatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:14.38,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Oh, Lain, if ask so many questions, your head is going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:20.06,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You’ve heard about people who lose a lot of weight because of stress, or go bald?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.26,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That’s psychosomatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:23.26,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lain, you don’t, by any chance…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.64,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,No, I don’t have that kind of problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:30.20,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Oh, I’m relieved. That was hasty of me!
